<keyLead id="30D695E30520621FFEF3309EF8958AD1" pageId="2" pageNumber="91">
5 (4). Venter of pterothorax with long pale hairs. Pectoral colour pattern with welldeveloped dark metasternal spots (fig. 8) .......................... 
<taxonomicName id="4C274D550520621FFA3330C8F92B8AD1" authority="J. Belle, 1997" authorityName="J. Belle" authorityYear="1997" box="[1461,1669,964,1004]" class="Insecta" family="Lestidae" genus="Lestes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="2" pageNumber="91" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="trichonus" status="spec. nov.">
