<emphasis id="B953EAC40520621FFA6430C8F92B8AD1" box="[1506,1669,964,1004]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="91">trichonus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A26057BF0520621FF91430C8F8958AD1" box="[1682,1851,964,1004]" pageId="2" pageNumber="91" rank="species">spec. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9836D60520621FFEF030FAF8928D72" blockId="2.[373,1871,462,1104]" pageId="2" pageNumber="91">
<keyLead id="30D695E30520621FFEF030FAF8928D72" pageId="2" pageNumber="91">
- Venter of pterothorax glabrous. Pectoral colour pattern without or with weakly developed dark metasternal spots ........................................... 
<taxonomicName id="4C274D550520621FFA67372BF8928D72" authorityName="Rambur" authorityYear="1842" box="[1505,1852,1063,1103]" class="Insecta" family="Lestidae" genus="Lestes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="2" pageNumber="90" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tenuatus">
